---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Policy - BGP.mom">
  <main class="w-full py-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          Policy for Adding Hosting Providers to BGP.mom Directory
        </h1>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <!-- Purpose Section -->
        <div class="card card-border bg-base-100 mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">
              <span class="badge badge-primary badge-outline">I.</span>
              Purpose
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
              The purpose of this policy is to outline the criteria for adding hosting providers to the BGP.mom directory. 
              This policy ensures that the listed providers offer affordable server options with BGP sessions specifically 
              tailored for newcomers and hobbyists.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Criteria Section -->
        <div class="card card-border bg-base-100 mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">
              <span class="badge badge-primary badge-outline">II.</span>
              Criteria for Hosting Providers
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-4">
              To be eligible for listing on the BGP.mom directory, hosting providers must meet the following criteria:
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-l-4 border-info pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Affordability:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-base-content/80">
                  <li>The provider must have a setup fee of under $50.</li>
                  <li>The lowest plan offered by the provider must be $10 or cheaper.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-success pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">BGP Session Availability:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base-content/80">
                  <li>The provider must offer BGP sessions.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-warning pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Quality of Service:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base-content/80">
                  <li>The provider must have a track record of reliable service, as determined by customer reviews and internal assessment.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-secondary pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Customer Support:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base-content/80">
                  <li>The provider should offer adequate customer support to assist users in setting up and managing their servers and BGP sessions.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-accent pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Legitimacy:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base-content/80">
                  <li>The provider must be a legitimate business entity, complying with the laws and regulations of its operating jurisdiction.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Listing Format Section -->
        <div class="card card-border bg-base-100 mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">
              <span class="badge badge-primary badge-outline">III.</span>
              Listing Format
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-4">
              Providers listed on BGP.mom will be displayed with the following information:
            </p>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="card card-border bg-base-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-primary mb-2">Provider Name</h4>
                  <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">Company or service name</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card card-border bg-base-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-primary mb-2">Plans and Pricing</h4>
                  <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">Including setup fees and monthly costs</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card card-border bg-base-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-primary mb-2">BGP Session Details</h4>
                  <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">Information on the BGP sessions offered</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card card-border bg-base-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-primary mb-2">Location Details</h4>
                  <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">Information on where the services are offered</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Policy Review Section -->
        <div class="card card-border bg-base-100 mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">
              <span class="badge badge-primary badge-outline">IV.</span>
              Policy Review
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
              This policy will be reviewed annually to ensure it continues to facilitate the directory's objective of 
              providing a reliable resource for finding affordable hosting providers with BGP sessions. Suggestions for 
              policy modifications can be submitted to the review team for consideration during the annual review.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information Section -->
        <div class="card card-border bg-base-100 mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">
              <span class="badge badge-primary badge-outline">V.</span>
              Contact Information
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
              For inquiries regarding this policy or listing your hosting provider, please 
              <a href="https://github.com/Bitti09/bgp.mom/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link link-primary">
                open an issue on GitHub
              </a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Effective Date Section -->
        <div class="card card-border bg-base-100 mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">
              <span class="badge badge-primary badge-outline">VI.</span>
              Policy Effective Date
            </h2>
            <div class="alert alert-info alert-outline">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p class="text-base-content">
                  This policy is effective as of <strong>20/07/2025 (DD/MM/YYYY)</strong> and supersedes all previous 
                  policies regarding the listing of hosting providers on the BGP.mom directory.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="card card-border bg-base-200">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
              <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-4 text-primary">Ready to Submit Your Provider?</h3>
              <p class="mb-6 text-base-content/90">
                If your hosting provider meets the criteria outlined above, we'd love to hear from you!
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-center gap-4">
                <a 
                  href="https://github.com/Bitti09/bgp.mom/issues/new?template=add-provider.yml" 
                  target="_blank" 
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
                >
                  Submit Provider
                </a>
                <a 
                  href="/" 
                  class="btn btn-outline btn-primary btn-lg"
                >
                  Browse Providers
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
